text: Novaya Kazanovka () is a rural locality (a village) in Denisovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 240 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Meleuz. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Novaya Kazanovka
